{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s001", "order": 1, "text": "**Feature Requirement Document: Destructive Intent Confirmation**\n\n**Feature Name:**", "char_start": 0, "char_end": 84, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 18}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s002", "order": 2, "text": "Destructive Intent Voice Confirmation and Safety Logging\n\n**Objective:**", "char_start": 85, "char_end": 160, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 14}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s003", "order": 3, "text": "To ensure user safety and prevent accidental data loss, a confirmation mechanism must be added when the detected user intent is classified as destructive, specifically when it matches the \"delete everything\" command.", "char_start": 160, "char_end": 378, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 38}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s004", "order": 4, "text": "**Requirements:**\n\n1.", "char_start": 378, "char_end": 399, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 8}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s005", "order": 5, "text": "**Intent Validation:**  \n   - Trigger confirmation flow only if the detected intent equals \"delete everything\".", "char_start": 400, "char_end": 517, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 23}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s006", "order": 6, "text": "- The detected intent must have a confidence score of **≥ 0.9** to proceed.", "char_start": 517, "char_end": 594, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 20}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s007", "order": 7, "text": "2. **User Confirmation:**  \n   - A verbal confirmation must be requested.", "char_start": 594, "char_end": 673, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 18}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s008", "order": 8, "text": "- The system must explicitly ask: *“Are you sure you want to delete everything?”", "char_start": 673, "char_end": 753, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 19}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s009", "order": 9, "text": "*  \n   -", "char_start": 753, "char_end": 761, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 3}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s010", "order": 10, "text": "The user must respond with an exact verbal **“yes”** to proceed.", "char_start": 762, "char_end": 826, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 18}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s011", "order": 11, "text": "Any other response cancels the action.", "char_start": 827, "char_end": 867, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 8}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s012", "order": 12, "text": "3.", "char_start": 867, "char_end": 869, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 2}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s013", "order": 13, "text": "**Event Logging:**  \n   - All such destructive intent actions must be logged to the `voice_safety` index.", "char_start": 870, "char_end": 981, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 24}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s014", "order": 14, "text": "- The log must include timestamp, user ID, intent string, confidence score, and confirmation response.", "char_start": 981, "char_end": 1085, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 21}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s015", "order": 15, "text": "4. *", "char_start": 1085, "char_end": 1089, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 3}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s016", "order": 16, "text": "*Rollback Capability:**", "char_start": 1089, "char_end": 1118, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 6}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s017", "order": 17, "text": "- A rollback option must be available for **10 minutes** post-execution.", "char_start": 1118, "char_end": 1196, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 19}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s018", "order": 18, "text": "- Rollback must reverse the “delete everything” operation entirely if invoked within the allowed window.", "char_start": 1196, "char_end": 1302, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 19}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s019", "order": 19, "text": "**Priority:** High  \n**Owner:** Voice Interaction Safety Team", "char_start": 1302, "char_end": 1363, "splitter": "spacy", "token_count": 16}
